Sentencas: The extensive explorations of potential cathode materials are prominently critical for the rapid development of high performance solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Herein, we develop a novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-delta (SCNC) cathode base on solid state reaction, which exhibits decent compatibility with gadolinium doped cerium oxide (GDC) electrolyte.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SCNC is successfully stabilized with cubic structure at room temperature when incorporating of small amount of high valence Nb5+.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Meanwhile, the oxygen vacancy concentration of SCNC is efficiently improved with the addition of Cu.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The Nb and Cu co-doping also substantially promotes the electronic conductivity, achieving 550 S cm(-1) for the optical doped SrCo0.85Nb0.05Cu0.10O3-delta (SCNC10) at 400 degrees C.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the polarization of SCNC is remarkably reduced, reaching as low as 0.021 Omega cm(2) for SCNC10 at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The activation energy for reaction is also significantly lowered to 0.78 eV.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The reaction order m is deduced to be about 0.30, implying that the rate determination step for SCNC10 is the charge transfer reaction.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The peak power density of the single cell reaches 780 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All these outstanding performances demonstrate that SCNC is a promising cathode for SOFCs when operating at intermediate temperature (IT).
Titulo: A novel Nb and Cu co-doped SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
